dooyit.parser

Class DeleteParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • dooyit.parser.TagParser
      • dooyit.parser.DeleteParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserCommons

    public class DeleteParser
extends TagParser
    The DeleteParser class takes in a "delete" or "remove" or "rm" command input and returns a Command object. It is needed for deleting tasks. It is a child class of the TagParser class.
    Author:
    Annabel
